 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/umar-dua-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":24600,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Umar ibn al-Khattab\u2019s supplication in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, would say these words aloud in prayer, \u201cGlory be to You, O Allah, with Your praises. Blessed is Your name, exalted is Your majesty. There is no God other than You.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 399 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/salman-king-not-a-khalifah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24600,"position":4},"title":"Salman on Khilafah: Unjust leaders are kings, not Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farisi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to him, \u201cAm I a king or a Caliph?\u201d Salman said, \u201cIf you acquire as much as two coins from the lands of the Muslims, more or less, then you place it where it does not belong,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"